://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/36158/', '', 'Tropicamide, Ephedrine, Ketorolac, Phenylephrine', 'Ciclesonide, Mometasone furoate, Budesonide, Flunisolide, Fluticasone, Cromoglicic acid, Betamethasone, Nedocromil, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 1767369485);
